Package: miloR
Type: Package
Title: Differential neighbourhood abundance testing on a graph
Version: 0.99.12
Authors@R:
    c(person("Mike", "Morgan", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="michael.morgan@cruk.cam.ac.uk"),
    person("Emma", "Dann", role=c("aut", "ctb"), email="ed6@sanger.ac.uk"))
Description: This package performs single-cell differential abundance testing by 
    modelling cell states as neighbourhoods on a nearest neighbour graph using a negative bionomial 
    generalized linear model.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://marionilab.github.io/miloR
